cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.GT, cs.HC

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the use of natural language processing techniques to generate and verify image captions.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper presents a game that uses AI to generate and verify image captions.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper deals with image captioning, which is a task in computer vision.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is relevant as the paper presents a game that collects image descriptions.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of human players to generate and verify image captions.
